@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@bookId = replace-with-book-id

### System

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Delay (default 1 second)
GET {{baseUrl}}/delay

### Delay (custom seconds)
GET {{baseUrl}}/delay?delay=3

### Books

### List all books
GET {{baseUrl}}/books

### Get book by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}

### Create book
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer",
  "author": "David Thomas",
  "year": 1999
}

### Create book (without year)
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin"
}

### Update book
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer (20th Anniversary Edition)",
  "year": 2019
}

### Delete book
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/books/{{bookId}}
